This is a placeholder file for a 3D model.
You need to replace this file with an actual .glb 3D model file.
You can download 3D models from sites like:
- Free3D.com
- Sketchfab.com
- Google Poly (archived)
- Or create your own using Blender and export as GLB format.

For testing, you can use any GLB file from:
https://github.com/KhronosGroup/glTF-Sample-Models/tree/master/2.0